<title>CROATIA: BASKETBALL-CHARLEROI SQUANDER BIG CHANCE.</title>
<headline>BASKETBALL-CHARLEROI SQUANDER BIG CHANCE.</headline>
<dateline>ZAGREB 1996-11-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Cibona Zagreb reversed a three-match EuroLeague losing streak on Thursday to see off hapless Charleroi of Belgium 75-66 but they made hard work of it.</p>
<p>At one stage in the second half the Belgians, without a European win in six previous matches this season, led by 10 points.</p>
<p>Then Cibona's playmaker Zdravko Radulovic stole a ball in his court, sank a two-pointer and another free throw.</p>
<p>Spurred on by the home fans , Cibona produced a 15-0 series to deny the Belgians.</p>
<p>Zagreb are back in the hunt in group B but Charleroi remain firmly at the bottom.</p>
